"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-news-2024-0405-1441811-olympic-pool-diver-slips\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"A French international diver has laughed off an embarrassing mishap in front of President Emmanuel Macron which saw him fall on the diving board and crash into the water at the inauguration of the aquatics centre for the 2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 243, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4, \"end\": 24, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9279322437848512, \"rank\": 0.07766324394418146, \"text\": \"French international\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 92, \"end\": 107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an embarrassing mishap\", \"from\": 45, \"to\": 67}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 71, \"to\": 76}, {\"ngram\": \"the diving board\", \"from\": 128, \"to\": 144}, {\"ngram\": \"crash\", \"from\": 149, \"to\": 154}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 160, \"to\": 169}, {\"ngram\": \"the inauguration\", \"from\": 173, \"to\": 189}, {\"ngram\": \"the aquatics centre\", \"from\": 193, \"to\": 212}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 217, \"to\": 240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alexis Jandard, a two-time world championship minor medallist, has won widespread praise on social media for gamely mocking his own misfortune rather than silently retreating into a corner.\", \"from\": 245, \"to\": 434, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Alexis Jandard\", \"from\": 245, \"to\": 259}, {\"ngram\": \"a two-time world championship minor medallist\", \"from\": 261, \"to\": 306}, {\"ngram\": \"widespread praise\", \"from\": 316, \"to\": 333}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 337, \"to\": 349}, {\"ngram\": \"his own misfortune\", \"from\": 369, \"to\": 387}, {\"ngram\": \"a corner\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 433}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Jandard, performing a synchronised routine on the three metre board with two other divers during the ceremony, lost his footing while jumping, landed painfully on the board on his back and bottom and then splashed into the water.\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 668, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mr Jandard\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 446}, {\"ngram\": \"a synchronised routine\", \"from\": 459, \"to\": 481}, {\"ngram\": \"the three metre board\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 506}, {\"ngram\": \"two other divers\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 528}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 548}, {\"ngram\": \"his footing\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 566}, {\"ngram\": \"the board\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 611}, {\"ngram\": \"his back\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 623}, {\"ngram\": \"bottom\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 634}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 667}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am fine really!\", \"from\": 670, \"to\": 688, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's superficial although it looks impressive on the images,\\\" Mr Jandard told BFMTV after waking up to discover yesterday's mishap had become a viral meme overnight.\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 854, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 767, \"end\": 772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BFMTV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the images\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"Mr Jandard\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 761}, {\"ngram\": \"yesterday's mishap\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 819}, {\"ngram\": \"a viral meme\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The fall was ridiculous... it's part of the game.\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 906, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The fall\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 865}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 893}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 905}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If I look at the fall it's funny.\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 940, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fall\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 928}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's something that happens to us in diving - not regularly but it's not surprising.\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 1027, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 976}, {\"ngram\": \"diving\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 986}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It happens in training sometimes, in competition.\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1077, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1050}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1076}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But there it was in front of the president during the inauguration of the pool.\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1157, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1103}, {\"ngram\": \"the president\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"the inauguration\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1144}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1156}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I told myself it was the worst moment!\\\"\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1197, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the worst moment\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1195}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said he had received a message from the president and the Minister of Sports Amelie Oudea-Castera had phoned him to ensure all was well.\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1338, \"en